# 🛠️ DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT RULES

**CRITICAL: These environment rules MUST be followed WITHOUT EXCEPTION.**

This project requires **Python 3.11+** and standardizes on [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) for environment management, dependency synchronization, and command execution.

You **MUST NOT manually activate Python virtual environments**. **ALWAYS use `uv run <command>`**.

---

