## 2. MONOREPO STRUCTURE

The project uses a **uv workspace monorepo** with independent packages bundled into a single distributable wheel.

### Workspace Layout

```
indexed/
├── pyproject.toml                 # Root workspace config
├── uv.lock                        # Locked dependencies (commit this!)
│
├── apps/indexed/                  # Main CLI application
│   ├── src/indexed/              # CLI commands, MCP server
│   └── pyproject.toml
│
├── packages/                      # Bundled packages
│   ├── indexed-core/             # Engine, indexing, search
│   ├── indexed-config/           # Configuration management
│   ├── indexed-connectors/       # Jira, Confluence, Files connectors
│   └── utils/                    # Shared utilities
│
├── tests/                         # Unit and integration tests
├── docs/                          # Development documentation
└── .cursor/rules/                # Context rules for AI agents
```

### Workspace Configuration

```toml
[tool.uv.workspace]
members = [
    "apps/indexed",
    "packages/indexed-core",
    "packages/indexed-config",
    "packages/indexed-connectors",
    "packages/utils",
]
```

Each package has its own `pyproject.toml` with independent dependencies and tests.

