## 8. GIT HOOKS

Pre-commit and pre-push hooks run automatically:

**Pre-commit hooks:**
- ruff linting
- ruff formatting

**Pre-push hooks:**
- Full test suite verification
- Wheel build verification

Install hooks:

```bash
uv run pre-commit install --hook-type pre-commit --hook-type pre-push
```

Hooks run across entire monorepo. They will block commits/pushes if violations are detected.

