## 11. TROUBLESHOOTING

### "Command not found: pytest"
✅ Use `uv run pytest`, not `pytest` directly.

### "ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'indexed'"
✅ Run `uv sync --all-groups` to install packages in editable mode.

### "Wheel build failed"
✅ Build from PROJECT ROOT: `uvx --from build pyproject-build --installer=uv --outdir=dist --wheel apps/indexed`

### "Module not found when importing workspace package"
✅ Verify package in root `pyproject.toml` workspace members list.

### "Tests pass locally, fail in CI"
✅ Ensure FULL test suite runs: `uv run pytest -q` (not partial subset).

### "Ruff misses issues"
✅ Run ruff from PROJECT ROOT: `uv run ruff check .` (not from package directory).

### "Dependency resolution conflicts"
✅ Update lock file: `rm uv.lock && uv sync --all-groups`

